For running the virtual environment:

Creating the environment to run fastapi and uvicorn in for the microservices
& "PROJECTDIRECTORYPATH systems\.venv\Scripts\python.exe" -m pip install fastapi uvicorn

Then activating the environment
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate


Installing other dependencies
pip install passlib[bcrypt] pyjwt requests



Running the microservices aka. the servicesRunner.py file
This command will run all the microservices at once on the machine

uvicorn servicesRunner:subApp --reload
